{"type": "article", "id": 24300, "title": "手工陶瓷小件", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-23T07:00:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702144103qNWKP8ZCzF4MwQoj.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一些手工做的陶瓷小件，来自英国的陶瓷艺术家 Jono Smart。他采用了浅棕和深棕两种颜色制作这些花瓶、碗、鸡蛋杯等生活常见的用品，形状简单而没有任何花纹，只是近距离看时可以看到细腻的环形纹路，有温柔的手感。设计师 Helen Osgerby 在 2015 启动了一个 Simple Shapes 的计划，邀请不同的设计师设计这些手工做的生活小件，<a href=\"http://www.simple-shape.com/shop/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144101EaqZ1vSIldUDXJxg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144101rLGIJhHVPYXu9mtl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144102qZsVkYR6IUga1bAL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144102vYJCBiMwoSgEVZxL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144103yIfpZNiKVrFQA2Uu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}